[A presentation (in Russian) on the 2010 ASF situation in Russia is
appended to the protocol above and can be seen at
<http://fsvps.ru/fsvps-docs/ru/iac/2011/files/asf_2011.pdf>

The declared intentions of the Russian authorities are far-reaching,
in particular the plan to eliminate the keeping and breeding of pigs
in holdings of all types and in private backyards within several
given regions. The Russian government will need very significant
financial and technical means, as well as political powers, in their
efforts to achieve such goals. - Mod.AS]

[St Petersburg can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail
interactive map of the Russian Federation at
<http://healthmap.org/r/0muQ>. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
